9.2 The class hierarchy for DUIM-Frames

9.2.4 Subclasses of <page>

Although the <page> class is itself a subclass of <gadget>, and is exposed by the DUIM-Gadgets library, two of its subclasses are exposed by the DUIM-Frames library: <wizard-page> and <property-page>. See Section 8.4.3 on page 512 for an introduction to these classes.
